Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃貓大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.86,0:00:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃貓大人  讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請享用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.40,0:00:25.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您還有什麼別的需要嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.67,0:00:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來有什麼吩咐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:52.80,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(455,105)\fad(500,500)}「因為是桃貓大人的憂鬱」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓也從圍牆上摔下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:52.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃貓大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為貓這還真是不合格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說剛才那不是很好的拍攝時機嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:03.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我擔心它有沒有受傷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.90,0:03:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該說桃貓大人是好像有超強的生命力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.95,0:03:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是該說臉皮厚到讓人肅然起敬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去完全沒問題不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像心情很差
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:25.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃貓大人  請就保持那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠還真是悠閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做貓真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.24,0:03:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想每天無所事事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是呢  變成貓的話好像就能夠爬到很多地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍下各種有趣的照片了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那去喝杯茶準備回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  走吧薰親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許叫我薰親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薰親～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:39.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你快給我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}真是太感謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:13.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不好意思  桃貓大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.18,0:05:28.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是野豬嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:31.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}請您無論如何幫幫忙！  桃貓大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.70,0:05:39.68,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}就交給我吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.02,0:06:16.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}明明說了要你幫忙的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.53,0:06:16.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}大騙子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:19.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}笨蛋笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:23.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}回去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.74,0:06:26.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}不…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}辦不到辦不到辦不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.02,0:07:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在本町4丁目那一帶好像又出現了野豬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 又出現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:19.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易長成的蔬菜似乎被吃掉不少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  拍到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:47.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}住手  今天不要拍我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪  走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.67,0:07:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:57.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得桃貓大人沒什麼精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.99,0:07:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不和平時沒什麼兩樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.67,0:08:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠無所事事還真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只要有桃貓大人在就覺得鬆了口氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確  感覺牠就是這一帶的神獸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是超有存在感呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃貓大人在的話就安心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  牠動了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牠要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪  走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和平時不太一樣耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  桃貓大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟蹋農田的就是那隻野豬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是來討伐牠的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:54.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我不會向別人說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你拉鉤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有肉球耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香親  這真是偶然的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.44,0:10:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能說是前世就有的姻緣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:18.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運啊  Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.11,0:10:21.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.48,0:10:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…糰子？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  這是勇者的肉球哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.45,0:10:29.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是肉球…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很帥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:32.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帥的肉球…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看不見哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香親的話語一片混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊什麼啊  紀惠我看見的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃貓大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去感覺好像不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:50.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楓  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去還要準備小考啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.49,0:10:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓不要考試和上學還真是好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.26,0:10:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是輕鬆啊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但貓也是很不容易的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再加「喵」玩貓語了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說順嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:17.88,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(505,105)\fad(500,500)}「因為是失戀相機」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  HOBORO店主的什錦燒無論什麼時候都是這麼好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…的廣島菜啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.94,0:11:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,題目就定為「熱情似火的冰冷瞬間」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光…臨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:02.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HOBORO燒…10個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10個？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您…是要帶回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就現在在這裡吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那那那那…那就給我來11個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就來12個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  那我就每人燒二十個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們可要一·個·不·剩地給我吃完哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.76,0:12:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒問題  我還能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,標題「為了重新站起來」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼啦  只是被醬汁熏到…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.37,0:13:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚…肚子好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.52,0:13:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.81,0:13:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是何方神聖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是偶爾來竹原的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人小姐  我們馬上就要打烊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:18.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚您在哪邊住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居無定所的  沒關係我露宿就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你在考慮些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.56,0:13:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒考慮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家現在沒有多的鋪蓋  沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.01,0:13:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還能再吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別在這裡吐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡是重要的建築群保護地區
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:50.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐代美小姐  不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  之前和這女孩在朝日山見到過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:14:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是發生了什麼啊  突然一個人開始大胃王比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正堂鄉不管什麼時候都是大胃王呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.12,0:14:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說塙同學  不要直呼以前班主任的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.62,0:14:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楓  是認識的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有偶爾遇到過一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二樓的鋪蓋已經準備好了  你們慢慢來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得好香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:41.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事情了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我也睡這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也來陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.21,0:14:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  好期待過夜…貝類中牡蠣還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂鄉  你給我回家去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了不要直呼我名字
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.87,0:15:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  得拜託理穗妹妹看家 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:23.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒問題  請不要管我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.89,0:15:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是愛逞強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告白的那個人在你那過夜了？  真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  昨晚很晚才來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況怎樣  告白還順利嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.00,0:15:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她早飯午飯都吃了很多  連甜點也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這豪吃的狀態是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.53,0:16:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊這邊  注意腳下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:08.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勞您費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻子  我在找你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚…肚子…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  她好像是吃太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然吃那麼多我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這量實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.73,0:16:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是小楓吧  之前我們見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫保志真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  她是飛田志麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是塙薰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:16:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫岡崎紀惠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是櫻田麻音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說志麻子小姐的告白怎麼樣了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼  告白是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憧憬之路那天  志麻子小姐說是要向喜歡的人告白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那麼  那之後告白成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…志麻子也算是努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:24.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:29.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然志麻子從初中起就一直就這麼想著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是對方說只把她當做朋友看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要自暴自棄  暴飲暴食啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許事實上他有無法對別人說的苦情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:46.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識的女性被謎之組織追趕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好一起逃到里約熱內盧去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是里約…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:18:13.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}妄想力迸發
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  但是實際上拒絕交往是因為他染指了壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:17:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就不想把她捲入其中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.62,0:18:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是裝作對她稍微有點意思的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定都買好了保險  然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻音  快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是有了妻子  無論如何也沒法說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:13.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  剛才我稍微一聽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都盡說些有的沒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你清醒著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧志麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.75,0:18:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  真奈美  你是特地來找我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:31.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我暫時去獨自旅行了  bye
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你甩下一條那樣的短信就不見了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我不擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:34.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了  過去的事情就隨他去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.28,0:18:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是今後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是要不要去好好玩一通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.08,0:18:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜風什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.47,0:18:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是開車來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.95,0:18:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還要去準備開店
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走  出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  坐上去  志麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很抱歉  大家就別跟來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為要進行大人的戀愛談話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:10.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就出發囉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  快…快停…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.92,0:19:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔跑起來就無法停止  這就是戀愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要下去  我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛沒有中途下車
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.79,0:19:32.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每時每刻都加速裝置全開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:36.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算一段戀情結束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就正有活著的感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:42.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}前方禁止通行  請在這裡返回
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果弄錯了返回就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看  景色真好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:00.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉那小小的心靈創傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:29.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那傢伙的照片  我全部都刪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一來到這裡就感覺打起精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奈美  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來拍個重新振作的我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:21:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我來拍的話只能拍出悲傷表情的志麻子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻子一直都在逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:08.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻子拍下的照片瞞不掉你的真實心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明偶爾大哭一場就好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷的時候  說出來又有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻子有多思念著他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:31.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達了一份怎樣的感情  我都知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.41,0:21:41.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明可以向我宣洩感情的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奈美…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這孩子和我永遠是志麻子的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:04.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奈美  你還是給我拍張照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍我這沒用的哭喪臉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.97,0:22:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是沒用呢  很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.04,0:22:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍下坦率而可愛的志麻子了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.18,0:22:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本該是悲傷的哭泣面龐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿在閃著炫目的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.27,0:22:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相機的不可思議又多了一個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.61,0:24:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  今天輕輕鬆鬆搞定20份
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.88,0:24:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  回到平常的志麻子了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.98,0:24:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那原來不是暴飲暴食…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.16,0:24:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是本來就是大胃王嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.29,0:24:34.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  玉響～hitotose～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.30,0:24:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「明天的我會是怎樣的我…呢」
